{"root":{"data":{"id":"d50jaytbapz4","created":1729417402662,"text":"辛普森多样性指数"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jbvo4jym8","created":1729417474182,"text":"群落中种数越多，各种个体分配越均匀，指数越低，群落多样性越高，对均匀度和群落中优势的OTU更敏感。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jc2x7xq80","created":1729417489970,"text":"计算公式","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jc9w24pvk","created":1729417505137,"text":"D=1−∑(pi^2​)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jcpdeiigw","created":1729417538837,"text":"D 是辛普森多样性指数，表示群落的多样性程度，值的范围在0到1之间。\n值越接近1，表示多样性越高；值越接近0，表示多样性越低"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jcudjt5a8","created":1729417549730,"text":"(pi) 是群落中第i个物种的相对丰度，即该物种在群落中的比例"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jny5340zk","created":1729418419931,"text":"∑(pi^2​)表示所有物种相对丰度的平方和"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d50jp0k8h0xs","created":1729418503565,"text":"例子"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jprj4skxs","created":1729418562272,"text":"样本1：均匀分布"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jqbiueakg","created":1729418605790,"text":"物种A: 33.3% ；物种B: 33.3% ；物种C: 33.3% "},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jrihacutc","created":1729418699297,"text":"D=0.667"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d50jpwr73t34","created":1729418573643,"text":"样本2：非均匀分布，物种A占主导地位"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jqo2yhpts","created":1729418633127,"text":"物种A: 60% ；物种B: 20% ；物种C: 20% "},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jrdnsxhc0","created":1729418688807,"text":"D=0.24"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d50jpy6ucf7k","created":1729418576766,"text":"样本3：稀有物种存在"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jr127sge8","created":1729418661381,"text":"物种A: 50% ；物种B: 40% ；物种C: 10% "},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jr9lxh6gw","created":1729418679987,"text":"D=0.49"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d50jrqr8d8u8","created":1729418717313,"text":"解释"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d50jrue7nn5s","created":1729418725233,"text":"样本1 显示了均匀分布的情况，辛普森多样性指数相对较高，表明群落多样性较高。 "},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d50jrxx4x5a8","created":1729418732907,"text":"样本2 显示了一个物种占主导地位，辛普森多样性指数较低，表明群落的均匀度较低。 